# Drift Guard

Infrastructure must match **SSOT** and **canonical topology.**

**SSOT:** docs/00-SSOT/v1  
**Canonical topology:** `.cursor/knowledge/infra_topology.yaml` — 서비스·큐·연결 정의. drift = 이 파일 또는 SSOT와 불일치.

**If drift detected:**

- Recommend **script fix** (scripts/v1 only; do not use scripts/archive)
- NOT manual console changes

**Rules:**

- Before creating a resource: check existence
- Prefer Ensure-* scripts
- Never blindly recreate infrastructure
